Type Command means Add Command or Done Command or Quit Command

Record Add Command
  Has Title as String

Record Done Command
  Has Id as Int

Record Quit Command

Make First be New Add Command with Title be "write tests" as Command
Make First Label be Match First
  When Add Command with Title be Title
    "add {Title}"
  When Done Command
    "done"
  When Quit Command
    "quit"
Expect First Label is "add write tests"

Make Second be New Done Command with Id be 7 as Command
Make Second Label be Match Second
  When Add Command
    "add"
  When Done Command named Done
    "done {Id of Done}"
  When Quit Command
    "quit"
Expect Second Label is "done 7"

Make Third be New Quit Command as Command
Make Third Label be Match Third
  When Add Command
    "add"
  When Done Command
    "done"
  When Quit Command
    "quit"
Expect Third Label is "quit"
